thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Edward Rocha

author: Edward Rocha
title: Edward Rocha
text: Was really surprised when i received my box got it at a discounted price so assumed my box contents would reflect the low pay in factor . That was not the case got alot of great gear & a cool sticker plus a tips and tricks booklet i changed species for 2nd box cant wait to see what i get. I love it. Because they send items i might not buy for myself so it broadens my lure scope.
